    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi, I think that in class Zend_Log in factory function should be instead of this code</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (!is_array(current($config))) {
  $log-&gt;addWriter(current($config));
} else {
  foreach($config as $writer) {
    $log-&gt;addWriter($writer);
  }
}
</code></pre>

<p>this:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (!is_array(current($config))) {
  $log-&gt;addWriter(current($config));
} else {
  foreach(current($config) as $writer) {
    $log-&gt;addWriter($writer);
  }
}
</code></pre>

<p>With this bug it is impossible to add more writers using Zend_Application_Resource_Log.</p>

<p>If I am wrong, please tell me how to solve it by other way. Thanks.</p>

